de.esoco.data

Class DownloadData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
      • de.esoco.data.DownloadData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.obrel.core.Relatable

    public class DownloadData
extends org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
    This class encapsulates the data and parameters for an HTTP file download. The actual download data must be provided by a function that generates or returns the data object on evaluation.
